{"tid":2139737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚9點半港台31 歷史二三事講香港保衛戰","createTime":"2020-08-04T13:03:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T14:22:29.000Z","uid":49359,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c65e216767bbcecdf6fa14246fd8e2b531fa9887","tid":2139737,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:03:34.000Z","msg":"榮獲奧斯卡金像獎最佳男配角獎的馬克&middot;懷倫斯，是位一直致力推動和平的演員。他將會追尋他外公奧斯蒙&middot;史堅拿於二戰中有近四年時間，被日軍俘虜成為戰俘的故事。<br />\n<br />\n曾在香港上海匯豐銀行工作的奧斯蒙，當年加入了香港義勇防衛軍，被捲入殘酷的香港保衛戰。沒有受過軍事訓練的他，在聖誕節當日被子彈擊中，成為戰俘。<br />\n<br />\n在這感人的紀錄片中，當馬克&middot;懷倫斯得知公公如何在香港被關進臭名遠播的戰俘營中，仍生存下來之後，對戰爭有了新的睇法。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/historyontuesdays/episode/690312\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fhistoryontuesdays%2Fepisode%2F690312&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd9KNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=2f17cc3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/historyontuesdays/episode/690312</a>"},{"pid":"9f8cb0c2e0a72bad8e198f96e749dd00e60a2bfe","tid":2139737,"uid":65089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b1c1810fc721ac796f2da9cbbfdedd2ec8aac7","tid":2139737,"uid":65089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"播啦"},{"pid":"608926264c84bc55b8127ad52ca5667657dda8f7","tid":2139737,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd9KNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=2a0f98e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv</a><br />\n直播"},{"pid":"26e10fa1a86d91d5187a74a40a8071007e2ea2e9","tid":2139737,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:37:14.000Z","msg